data.description: Check out this raised ranch home! A lot of great updates in the last three years with a new furnace, ac, roof and siding. This home features three bedrooms with a full bath on the main level and full bath on the lower level. Off of the kitchen/dining room is a great additional sunroom that leads to your fenced in yard. This home has NEW solar panels that will pass on big savings to the new buyer!
